<http://www.spektrix.com/ccoa/event/289601ADHGJPVGKRHDNVVMJPTJMPPTGQT> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "2026 Symons Medal Presentation";
  schema:description """
	The Confederation Centre of the Arts is proud to announce The Honourable Justice Rosalie Silberman Abella as the winner of the 2026 Symons Medal.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>A former Justice of the Supreme Court of Canada, Justice Abella is internationally recognized for her leadership in equality and human rights, including her groundbreaking work on employment equity and her influential jurisprudence on Canada’s highest court.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Friday, September 25, 2026 – 1:00 p.m.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
